<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="74" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">
27. 
<taxonomicName LSID="E9A0FBEB-737E-6CE2-D184-34552C399F86" authority="(Bates, 1874)" baseAuthorityName="Bates" baseAuthorityYear="1874" class="Insecta" family="Cicindelidae" genus="Lophyra" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lophyra hilariola" order="Coleoptera" pageId="31" pageNumber="74" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hilariola">Lophyra hilariola (Bates, 1874)</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="74" type="habitat">
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">Habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">
On sparsely vegetated escarpments along rivers (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" author="Franzen, M" journalOrPublisher="Zoology in the Middle East" pageId="41" pageNumber="84" pagination="87 - 92" refId="B48" refString="Franzen, M, Bischoff, W, 1995. Ein Nachweis von Lophyra hilariola (Bates, 1874) aus Syrien (Carabidae: Cicindelinae). Zoology in the Middle East 11: 87 - 92, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" title="Ein Nachweis von Lophyra hilariola (Bates, 1874) aus Syrien (Carabidae: Cicindelinae)." url="https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" volume="11" year="1995">Franzen and Bischoff 1995</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="74" type="phenology">
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">Phenology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">
Poorly known, records from April and May, but may have a longer activity period (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" author="Franzen, M" journalOrPublisher="Zoology in the Middle East" pageId="41" pageNumber="84" pagination="87 - 92" refId="B48" refString="Franzen, M, Bischoff, W, 1995. Ein Nachweis von Lophyra hilariola (Bates, 1874) aus Syrien (Carabidae: Cicindelinae). Zoology in the Middle East 11: 87 - 92, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" title="Ein Nachweis von Lophyra hilariola (Bates, 1874) aus Syrien (Carabidae: Cicindelinae)." url="https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" volume="11" year="1995">Franzen and Bischoff 1995</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="74" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">Distribution range.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">
From Turkey to Iran (
<bibRefCitation author="Wiesner, J" journalOrPublisher="Entomologia Basiliensia" pageId="45" pageNumber="88" pagination="113 - 114" refId="B113" refString="Wiesner, J, 1988. Lophyra (s.str.) hilariola (Bates, 1874) neu fuer die Tuerkei. Entomologia Basiliensia 12: 113 - 114" title="Lophyra (s. str.) hilariola (Bates, 1874) neu fuer die Tuerkei." volume="12" year="1988">Wiesner 1988</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="31" pageNumber="74" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">Distribution in the southern Levant.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="31" pageNumber="74">No record.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="32" pageNumber="75" type="taxonomic notes">
<paragraph pageId="32" pageNumber="75">
<pageBreakToken pageId="32" pageNumber="75" start="start">Taxonomic</pageBreakToken>
notes.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="32" pageNumber="75">
A table found in 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" author="Franzen, M" journalOrPublisher="Zoology in the Middle East" pageId="41" pageNumber="84" pagination="87 - 92" refId="B48" refString="Franzen, M, Bischoff, W, 1995. Ein Nachweis von Lophyra hilariola (Bates, 1874) aus Syrien (Carabidae: Cicindelinae). Zoology in the Middle East 11: 87 - 92, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" title="Ein Nachweis von Lophyra hilariola (Bates, 1874) aus Syrien (Carabidae: Cicindelinae)." url="https://doi.org/10.1080/09397140.1995.10637676" volume="11" year="1995">Franzen and Bischoff (1995)</bibRefCitation>
can be used to differentiate 
<taxonomicName genus="L." lsidName="L. hilariola" pageId="32" pageNumber="75" rank="species" species="hilariola">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="75">L. hilariola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<taxonomicName genus="L." lsidName="L. flexuosa" pageId="32" pageNumber="75" rank="species" species="flexuosa">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="32" pageNumber="75">L. flexuosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
